    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Violas d'amore made around 1780 by Thomas Perry of Dublin, with a body about the size of a viola d'amore and five pairs of metal strings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
